track.name: Dust Bowl
comments: Joe Bonamassa is Guitar Wizard. With his music, he will send you to a flight of melody, romance, emotions, speed and fantasy
the normal Rx is slow the music down/speed living up - drinking lots of Jack while smoking like a train.... he's doing just fine as is!!   *L*
Joe earned his chops long ago- and we're all enjoying the fruits of his labor... :)

When I first heard this track when it was released, it took me by surprise. After the second listen, I thought it was such a killer cool track. Now when I hear the different live versions, I realize it is one of my favorite Jobo tracks. Bravo, Joe.
I like the fact that Joe B comes to Europe on a regular basis. It must be difficult with all those guitars!
Into the ideology of this musical impressionist firmly merged line of calm and ideal music and organically entered into its world human.
Always love when Bonamassa comes up in the rotation.
